==English==
===Etymology===
probably from reference to a board game
===Phrase===
'''back to square one'''
# back to the [[start]], as after a [[dead-end]] or [[failure]]
#: ''After spending six hours on the intake we realized that there was nothing wrong with it; I guess it's '''back to square one.''''
